    "name": "Dungeons of Eternity",
    "steam_appid": 3189340,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奇幻世界里的无尽动作冒险正在《Dungeons of Eternity》中等待你和你的朋友们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VR赋予砍杀游戏全新含义：挥剑、飞斧、拉弓射箭、挥舞法杖、自由发挥，杀出重围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当宇宙级别的灾难威胁到你的母星时，唯一的生存希望就潜藏在被遗弃的永恒之星上那些无尽的地下城中。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >合作或单人游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最多可与3名玩家共同冒险，获得难忘的合作体验，也可单独深入地下城。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189340/extras/77189e93bb499288d106e9065ea0f8a7.poster.avif?t=1769632774\" width=1170 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189340/extras/77189e93bb499288d106e9065ea0f8a7.webm?t=1769632774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189340/extras/77189e93bb499288d106e9065ea0f8a7.mp4?t=1769632774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不断变化的地下城</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索结合多种游戏模式和领域随机生成的地下城——每次探索都独一无二。从战斗竞技场、解谜、陷阱房到密室，各式各样的地下城房间等你来闯。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189340/extras/8ac3ec5bc4ea74f0ce3134999cf81b07.poster.avif?t=1769632774\" width=1170 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189340/extras/8ac3ec5bc4ea74f0ce3134999cf81b07.webm?t=1769632774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189340/extras/8ac3ec5bc4ea74f0ce3134999cf81b07.mp4?t=1769632774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >亲身感受地下城</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于物理引擎的拟真战斗系统和游戏世界中的逼真互动，为你带来前所未有的砍杀体验。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189340/extras/1f4e810d35974bf144f2d49201be5f4f.poster.avif?t=1769632774\" width=1170 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189340/extras/1f4e810d35974bf144f2d49201be5f4f.webm?t=1769632774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189340/extras/1f4e810d35974bf144f2d49201be5f4f.mp4?t=1769632774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无尽武器库 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有武器均为随机生成，这就意味着你可以在地下城中找到几乎无尽的战利品。包括以下各种武器类型：剑、弓、法杖等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189340/extras/93103b50e18bfe03ef229e22a9ef76bc.poster.avif?t=1769632774\" width=1170 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189340/extras/93103b50e18bfe03ef229e22a9ef76bc.webm?t=1769632774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189340/extras/93103b50e18bfe03ef229e22a9ef76bc.mp4?t=1769632774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >个性玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过装备组合、升级和角色自定义选项来打造只属于你的游戏风格和角色外观。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189340/extras/ac919b510d6f04861bbb5b5edbd9a849.poster.avif?t=1769632774\" width=1170 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189340/extras/ac919b510d6f04861bbb5b5edbd9a849.webm?t=1769632774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189340/extras/ac919b510d6f04861bbb5b5edbd9a849.mp4?t=1769632774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
